data.description: USDA Eligible! Charming brick home located in Imperial Lakes. This home is in move in ready condition with many recent updates. 3 large Bedrooms and 2 baths. The side entry 2 car garage and a large driveway will fit all of your parking needs. Enjoy sitting on your back porch that over looks your large lawn with mature landscaping. The living area is open with plenty of natural lighting. Located close to many amenities such as grocery stores, restaurants, banks, pharmacies, and schools. This home is a must see to truly appreciate.
